      "title": "7 Covid deaths",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Director General of Health Services says that 7 deaths due to Covid have been reported yesterday (1).",
        "According to the report of the Director General of Health Services, three men over 60 years, two women and two women between 30 and 59 years have died.",
        "So far, the total number of Covid deaths reported in the country is 16,559."
      ],
